Constituent empowerment is about transforming your organization's mild supporters to passionate organizers for your cause.
1. Supporters read your correspondence via mail, email or social network activity but are rarely compelled to respond or donate. BEEx challenges create impetus for your supporters to donate NOW.
2. Donors are often interested in doing more to support your organization but don’t know how. BEEx makes it easy for them to create exciting personal fundraisers that will appeal to their individual social networks.
3. Fundraisers are comfortable asking their networks to support your organization. BEEx enables them to go a step further by asking their networks to create their own fundraising pages with our cluster tool.
4. Organizers of grassroots fundraising events can generate a lot of revenue for your nonprofit organization. We provide tools that empower your passionate supporters to do just that.

